text: The Turkmenistan women's national handball team is the national team of Turkmenistan. It is governed by the Handball Federation of Turkmenistan and takes part in international handball competitions. ==Asian Championship record== * 2002 – 6th * 2012 – 10th ==External links== *IHF profile Category:Women's national handball teams Handball National team
title: Turkmenistan women's national handball team
